Classes in com.fluidops.fedx.evaluation.join that implement ParallelExecutor
 class ControlledWorkerBoundJoin
          Execute the nested loop join in an asynchronous fashion, using grouped requests, i.e. group bindings into one SPARQL request using the UNION operator.
 class ControlledWorkerJoin
          Execute the nested loop join in an asynchronous fashion, i.e. one binding after the other (but concurrently) The number of concurrent threads is controlled by a ControlledWorkerScheduler which works according to the FIFO principle.
 class JoinExecutorBase<T>
          Base class for any join parallel join executor.
 class SynchronousBoundJoin
          Execute the nested loop join in a synchronous fashion, using grouped requests, i.e. group bindings into one SPARQL request using the UNION operator
 class SynchronousJoin
          Execute the nested loop join in a synchronous fashion, i.e. one binding after the other
